  "content": "# 3. Verify libcudnn (install if missing)\n\n### CUDA Installation\n\nUses NVIDIA's apt repository for Debian Trixie (matching the `rust:1.88-trixie` base image). Installs `cuda-toolkit-12-x` and `libcudnn9-dev`. Approximately 2GB download.\n\n\n### Failure Modes\n\n| Condition | Message |\n|-----------|---------|\n| No `nvidia-smi` | \"No NVIDIA GPU detected. Ensure NVIDIA drivers are installed on the host and GPU passthrough is configured.\" |\n| WSL2 without GPU | Check `/usr/lib/wsl/lib/libcuda.so` exists |\n| No network | \"Cannot download CUDA toolkit. Check internet connectivity.\" |\n| Download fails | Fall back to source build with `--features cuda` |\n",
